item.title: Nearly Crashed on Mulholland Snake
item.description:
Nearly Crashed on Mulholland Snake

Had a couple close calls on this run up the snake. Not sure if I could have saved it without the Diavel's assists kicking in. It happened suddenly and the entire bike wagged. If you're on social media.
